cast.overview: Ash, a handsome, shotgun-toting, chainsaw-armed department store clerk, is time warped backwards into England's Dark Ages, where he romances a beauty and faces legions of the undead.
cast.title: Army of Darkness

crew.overview: Novalee Nation is a 17-year-old Tennessee transient who has to grow up in a hurry when she's left pregnant and abandoned by her boyfriend on a roadside, and takes refuge in the friendly aisles of Wal-Mart. Eventually, some eccentric but kindly strangers 'adopt' Novalee and her infant daughter, helping them buck the odds and build a new life.
crew.title: Where the Heart Is

crew.overview: After kidnapping a father and his two kids, the Gecko brothers head south to a seedy Mexican bar to hide out in safety, unaware of its notorious vampire clientele.
crew.title: From Dusk Till Dawn

crew.original_title: Don't Be a Menace to South Central While Drinking Your Juice in the Hood
crew.overview: When Ashtray moves to South Central L.A. to live with his father (who appears to be the same age he is) and grandmother (who likes to talk tough and smoke reefer), he falls in with his gang-banging cousin Loc Dog, who along with the requisite pistols and Uzi carries a thermo-nuclear warhead for self-defense. Will Ashtray be able to keep living the straight life?
crew.title: Don't Be a Menace to South Central While Drinking Your Juice in the Hood

details.biography: Nadine Grycan is a stunt actor and actress known for From Dusk Till Dawn (1996), End of Days (1999) and Army of Darkness (1992).
details.name: Nadine Grycan
